# LaravelPizza - Project Identity Rules

## CRITICAL: Project Mission
This is a CONVERSION and ENHANCEMENT of https://laravelpizza.com/
NOT a replica - an IMPROVED, premium version.

Goals: More Cool | More Clickbait | More Engaging | More Viral

## Architecture
- Folio + Volt (NO controllers for front-office)
- CMS-driven pages (JSON content blocks)
- XotBase pattern (NEVER extend Filament directly)
- One table, one migration rule

## ServiceProvider Pattern (CRITICAL!)
ALWAYS use minimal structure:
- Extend XotBase* classes (XotBaseServiceProvider, XotBaseEventServiceProvider, etc.)
- Include ALL required properties: $name, $module_dir, $module_ns
- NO boot()/register() if only calling parent
- ALWAYS call parent::boot() FIRST if overriding
- Use #[Override] attribute

See: laravel/Modules/Xot/docs/serviceprovider-minimal-structure.md

## Quality Standards
- PHPStan level 10
- Laravel Pint (PSR-12)
- declare(strict_types=1);
- Documentation lowercase-with-hyphens.md

## Enhancement Mindset
Always ask: "Is this cooler than the original?"
Every feature should be share-worthy.

See: CLAUDE.md, laravel/CLAUDE.md, .ai-context/REMEMBER.md, .ai-context/provider-rules.md
